1061
01:22:47,600 --> 01:22:51,600
- Don't roll your eyes. Have you thought?

1062
01:22:51,600 --> 01:22:54,600
- What exactly am I supposed to think about?

1063
01:22:54,600 --> 01:22:56,599
- What are we going to do if I get pregnant?

1064
01:22:56,600 --> 01:22:59,600
- But you won't .

1065
01:22:59,600 --> 01:23:02,600
- How do you know I'm not already?

1066
01:23:02,600 --> 01:23:06,600
- Are you?

1067
01:23:07,600 --> 01:23:08,599
- You have no idea when I'm due for my period.

1068
01:23:08,600 --> 01:23:11,600
- I do know. Sometime these days, right?

1069
01:23:11,600 --> 01:23:13,599
- What do you care? It's not your problem.

1070
01:23:13,600 --> 01:23:17,600
- Why are you saying that?

1071
01:23:17,300 --> 01:23:21,300
- Did it ever happen while we were together?

1072
01:23:22,300 --> 01:23:24,299
- Take Thursday, I asked you to take care, and come outside.

1073
01:23:24,300 --> 01:23:25,299
