1129
01:27:32,400 --> 01:27:36,400
Could you tell me, did anybody go up to 206?

1130
01:27:37,400 --> 01:27:41,400
I'm Mihartescu, you talked to me in the morning.

1131
01:27:41,400 --> 01:27:44,400
No, no, you don't have to go up.

1132
01:27:44,400 --> 01:27:48,400
Thank you.

1133
01:27:53,400 --> 01:27:54,399
I have to go.

1134
01:27:54,400 --> 01:27:58,400
